===========================================================
This tool was developped by Eric Maisonnave (Cerfacs) 
to perform an analysis of the coupled components load balance
===========================================================
In /oasis3-mct/util/lucia, compile main-lucia.F90 : 
* first add your compiler by modifying "F90=my_compiler" 
in lucia
* compile using the command : lucia -c
* creation of the executable lucia.exe

In your results directory, post-treat of files lucia.MM.PPPPP :
* /oasis3-mct/util/lucia/lucia : this command will post-treat
all the lucia.MM.PPPPP located in the directory using lucia.exe


For more details, see the document XXX
 
